{"url": "https://www.ics.uci.edu/~kobsa/courses/ICS104/course-notes/error-avoidance.htm", "content": "<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/strict.dtd\">\n<html><head>\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n  <meta content=\"text/html; charset=ISO-8859-1\" http-equiv=\"content-type\"><title>Error avoidance</title></head><body>\n<big><big><font size=\"+3\"><big><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><b>Error\navoidance</b></font></big></font></big><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n</big>\n<ul><big>\n\n  </big><li style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><font size=\"+3\">Design\nthe user\ninterface in such a way that the user can easily build a <span style=\"font-style: italic;\">correct</span> mental model of how the\nsystem works<b> <br>\n\n    </b><img style=\"width: 31px; height: 20px;\" alt=\"Finger pointing right\" src=\"../../../graphics/pointing-finger-right3.jpg\">&nbsp; Use good metaphors<br>\n</font><font size=\"+3\"><img style=\"width: 31px; height: 20px;\" alt=\"Finger pointing right\" src=\"../../../graphics/pointing-finger-right3.jpg\">&nbsp; Use good affordances</font><br>\n</li><font size=\"+3\">\n  </font><li style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><font size=\"+3\">Provide\nlots of <i>advance information <br>\n\n    </i></font></li><font size=\"+3\">\n  </font><li style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><font size=\"+3\">Be\nflexible\nwith the input format<a target=\"_self\"> </a><a href=\"enforce-two-decimals.mov\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 21px; height: 27px;\" alt=\"The linked image shows how an interface unnecessarily inforces a specific format (2 decimal places)\" src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down-small.png\"></a><br>\n\n\n    </font></li><font size=\"+3\">\n  </font><li style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><font size=\"+3\">Dangerous\noptions should not be the default&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></li><font size=\"+3\">\n  </font><li style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><font size=\"+3\">Keep\ndangerous\nitems/icons away from frequently used commands.</font></li><font size=\"+3\">\n  \n  </font><li style=\"font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\"><font size=\"+3\">Warn\nusers if\nactions have irreversible effects, and request\nreconfirmation (which should not be the default option). <a href=\"error-are-you-sure.jpg\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 21px; height: 27px;\" alt=\"Error &quot;are you sure?&quot;\" src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down-small.png\"> </a><font><font><a href=\"dangerous-option-is-default.png\"><img src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 21px; height: 27px;\"></a></font></font></font></li><big>\n  </big></ul>\n\n<font size=\"+3\"><br>\n<br>\n</font>\n\n\n\n<p><font size=\"+3\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n\n</body></html>", "encoding": "ascii"}